Title: Wilderness
Author: Robert B. Parker
Published: Jun 2011
Publisher: Dell Publishing
ISBN: 978-0-307-57088-8
Format: Epub (Retail)
Language: English
Genres: Fiction, Suspense, Thriller


At 46, Aaron Newman was enjoying the good things in life - a good marriage, a good job - and he was in good shape himself. Then he saw the murder. A petty vicious killing that was to plunge him into an insane jungle of raw violence and fear, threatening and defiling the things he cared about.
While out jogging, suspense writer Aaron Newman witnesses a murder and notifies the police. When the suspect, psychopath Adolph Karl, threatens Newman's family, Aaron, his wife, and army buddy decide that their only chance is to eliminate Karl and his gang.
